{"title":"centos下离线安装sqlserver 无网络安装sqlserver","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.049Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/centos下离线安装sqlserver 无网络安装sqlserver","updated":"2023-07-28T09:18:50.963Z","content":"<p>首先下载离线资源包<br>\n<a href=\"https://download.csdn.net/download/u014292402/86401518\" target=\"_blank\">https://download.csdn.net/download/u014292402/86401518</a><br>\n<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/1b9020303de44cfaa1fda6179734028d.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<p>包中有4个文件，<strong>按如下顺序安装</strong>，否则可能会报依赖库缺失的错，导致功能不全</p>\n<p>1、首先安装mssql-server-14.0.3030.27-1.x86_64.rpm</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum localinstall mssql-server-14.0.3030.27-1.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>然后根据命令行提示，执行</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#配置sqlserver</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo /opt/mssql/bin/mssql-conf setup</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#第一个输入3，选择免费版</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#第二个输入你自己的密码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>2、再安装unixODBC-utf16-2.3.1-1.x86_64.rpm</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum localinstall unixODBC-utf16-2.3.1-1.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>3、再安装msodbcsql-13.0.1.0-1.x86_64.rpm</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum localinstall msodbcsql-13.0.1.0-1.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>4、最后安装mssql-tools-14.0.1.246-1.x86_64.rpm</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yum localinstall mssql-tools-14.0.1.246-1.x86_64.rpm</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>安装完成后</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#找到sqlcmd在哪个目录</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">find / -name sqlcmd</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#执行查找到的文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"variable\">$&#123;路径&#125;</span>/sqlcmd -U sa</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#输入你的密码就可以登陆sqlserver了</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/d2e931747f474f6d967172ca54afae06.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n<p>=========================================================<br>\n下面是sqlserver开启远程登陆</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#首先开启防火墙的1433端口</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --zone=public --add-port=1433/tcp --permanent</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#重启防火墙</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">firewall-cmd --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>在navicat中，新建sqlserver连接<br>\n输入地址和用户名、密码即可连接</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/d286bca3bc694d45939ab57f00e48b13.png\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"φbp\"></p>\n","prev":{"title":"centos7配置本地yum源","link":"2023/07/28/centos7配置本地yum源"},"next":{"title":"debian10中文乱码的问题","link":"2023/07/28/debian10中文乱码的问题"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/centos下离线安装sqlserver 无网络安装sqlserver/","reading_time":"355 字约 2 分钟"}